#. Description of the plugin
#: crumbler-cookie-consent.php
msgid "Connects your website to the Crumbler cookie consent service: consent banner, automatic script & iframe blocking, cookie declaration and Google Consent Mode v2."
msgstr "Verbindet Ihre Website mit dem Crumbler Cookie-Consent-Dienst: Consent-Banner, automatisches Script- & iFrame-Blocking, Cookie-Erklärung und Google Consent Mode v2."

